[[!tag Energy_Drink Review]]

This is one of seveal Tru Energy drinks from Tru, who also make health and
nootropic "focus" drinks like [[Tru_Focus_Apple_Kiwi]], the only difference with
those being they contain l-theanine. Tru is not widely distributed where I am,
but you can order them directly from their
[store](https://drinktru.com/collections/store) online.

