This Tru is light and bubbly. The carbonation makes the drink feel velvety
inside my mouth. It's a pleasant texture. As for taste, it's fittingly bright
and dry and partway between a peach and dried mango. A bit sour too. Very easy
to drink and quite good. I'm surprised I have not seen this drink around more
often. They compete in the same niche as Celsius so maybe this makes sense.

